{"tid":2323882,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[重開]有冇黃店賣聖誕卡（入俾收押手足）","createTime":"2020-12-13T13:36:36.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-13T16:35:41.000Z","uid":45295,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"79093bc0e5c0b2ad6997a78d4bd19ad72df2f07a","tid":2323882,"uid":45295,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-13T13:36:36.000Z","msg":"頭先開錯台<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n因為聖誕節就嚟 我有位朋友收押緊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n其實除咗出面嘅人可以寫聖誕卡寄入去<br />\n探訪親友可以入日用品嗰時入10張聖誕卡連信封 俾佢寄返出嚟<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"red\">但有好多限制<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/ohno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n1. 不可有任何附貼物，如絲帶、喱士、閃粉、貼紙等<br />\n2. 不可有額外裝置，如音樂裝罝、彈弓裝置、閃燈裝置等<br />\n3. 不可是立體設計、迷你咭，摺紙、有夾層（即兩層紙黐埋一層）<br />\n4. 尺寸不可大於 A4</span><br />\n<br />\n即係其實要普普通通嘅聖誕卡<br />\n但我個收押朋友又話唔想要太醜樣/卡通嗰啲<br />\n同時我又唔想去三中商/藍店買<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"x-large\"><strong>請問有冇黃店/ig shop有賣聖誕卡？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></strong></span>"},{"pid":"23436042d5aa1f8cfc3fb0f78c7fb43f00b594da","tid":2323882,"uid":357031,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-13T13:47:19.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://linktr.ee/Error505\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Flinktr.ee%2FError505&d=S6zCjV1yqQRAjAhc4t20mcls9Dgy9T8na9BfJ9hiblc%3D&h=2ea517f9\" target=\"_blank\">linktr.ee/Error505</a><br />\n<br />\n自己印 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ee550aa20c53b2cc2f084c987856232d1689a2b1","tid":2323882,"uid":357031,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-13T14:19:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3d0c9c44c0ae5826ecdae39806895615c9ea0d32","tid":2323882,"uid":244889,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-13T16:35:41.000Z","msg":"有啲黃店有聖誕咭文宣攞㗎"}]}